# dnd_mud verification

Console MUD — browser/IronBee tools **forbidden** (overrides global `browser-automation.mdc`).
Verification: `make test` + console smoke only.

## Git scope

Workflow, sync, commits, push, PR — [`01-operations.mdc`](~/.cursor/rules/01-operations.mdc).

**Обязательно** commit/push для задач с изменением кода или данных (не docs-only / comments-only).

**Не коммитить:** `.coverage`, `saves/` (персонажи и runtime state).

## Before finishing

1. **Git** — см. `01-operations.mdc` (Git-старт, sync); `git push -u origin HEAD` после задачи; не `main`/`dev`; clean working tree (кроме `.coverage`, `saves/`)
2. **`make test`** — after any code or data change
3. **`make check`** — when changing types, style, or public APIs
4. **Console smoke** — `python main.py`, затронутое меню

Implement first, verify once at the end. Skip runtime verify for docs-only changes.

Do not use browser DevTools / IronBee. Do not treat reading code alone as sufficient verification.
